        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for a copy of <hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi>.</p>  
<p>Describes experiment on <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> carried out with his pupils.</p> 
            <p>Describes reception of the book at the University of Zurich.</p>
            <p>Comments on Nägeli’s concept of a "morphological species".</p>
            <p>Expresses belief in importance of natural selection.</p> 
<p>Mentions his forthcoming publication ["Ulothrix zonata", <hi rend="italic">Jahrb. f. wiss. Bot.</hi> 10 (1876): 417–550].</p> 
        </abstract>
